            <head>Translation</head>
            <p>[Kollam year 10]78, month of Tulā, 27th day. As desired by Kṛṣṇavāddhyār
               (°vaddhyārkka, emend into °vaddhyārkku), [son of] Ve[kiṭīśvaravāddhyār], Rāmapaṭṭar
               copied (°lakhitam, emend into °likhitam) [it] with his own hand.” </p>
